snippet.title: Living in a Tiny House for 24 Hours!!!
snippet.description:
24 Hour Challenge Living in a Tiny House!!!
Check out Madison and Beyond: http://tinyurl.com/madisonsub
Subscribe to Trinity and Beyond: http://tinyurl.com/trinitysub
Check out our Newest Video: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=r2vKrOO_ecA&list=PLH2I3pcDbffEVSMcjBSVzxmw_s_-zBrnE

Spending 24 hours In My Mini Mansion Tiny House Shed!!! Today Trinity decided to try out a fun challenge and spend 24hrs in her tiny house! Good thing she made it like home. It's complete with a bed, weights for working out,  a tv and even a nintendo switch to play games on. The only thing missing is some snacks! Lucky for her, Madison and her friend Delanie show up with snacks. The girls also open the new Trinity and Beyond series 2 mystery jewelry box! They splay some more kart racers on the switch and before she knows it, it's dark out and time for bed!
